import React from 'react'
import TextEditor from './components/TextEditor'
import {v4 as uuidV4} from 'uuid'
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route,
  Redirect
} from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route path="/" exact>
          <Redirect to={`/documents/${uuidV4()}`}/>
        </Route>
        <Route path="/documents/:id" >
          <TextEditor/>
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
